                        <h2 class="my-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Generative AI and Machine Learning</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Enhance your business with advanced AI-driven tools designed to simplify processes, generate insights, and create value seamlessly.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-left">
                      <svg class="size-5 text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
                        <g fill="currentColor">
                          <path d="m224 80l-96 56l-96-56l96-56Z" opacity="0.2"/>
                          <path d="M230.91 172a8 8 0 0 1-2.91 10.91l-96 56a8 8 0 0 1-8.06 0l-96-56A8 8 0 0 1 36 169.09l92 53.65l92-53.65a8 8 0 0 1 10.91 2.91M220 121.09l-92 53.65l-92-53.65a8 8 0 0 0-8 13.82l96 56a8 8 0 0 0 8.06 0l96-56a8 8 0 1 0-8.06-13.82M24 80a8 8 0 0 1 4-6.91l96-56a8 8 0 0 1 8.06 0l96 56a8 8 0 0 1 0 13.82l-96 56a8 8 0 0 1-8.06 0l-96-56A8 8 0 0 1 24 80m23.88 0L128 126.74L208.12 80L128 33.26Z"/></g></svg>
                        <h2 class="my-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Application Development</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">From vision to deployment, build scalable, modern applications tailored to your goals, with attention to uniqueness, reliability, and user experience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-left">
                      <svg class="size-5 text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 0 0 1.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 0 1-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 0 1-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 0 1-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 1 0-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18" />
                      </svg>
                      
                        <h2 class="my-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Consulting</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Clear, actionable strategies for technology adoption and optimization, ensuring your business is always a step ahead.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>